# Amazon  Athena

                Serverless query servisse analyze data store in S3

                Standard SQL language

                Support CSV, JSON,ORC, AVRO and Parquet

                Commonly used with Amazon Quicksight for reporting/dashboard

 

                Use cases: BI / Analytics / query VPC flow logs, ELB logs, Cloud trail

 

# Athena Performance Improvement

                Compress data * use larger files >128MB

 

# Athena Federated Query

                Allows run SQL queries across data stored in relational or no relational database and data sources (AWS/on-premises)

 

# Redshift

                Based on PostgreeSQL

                OLAP – online analytical processing (analytics and warehousing)

                10x performance

 

                Snapshot & DR

                               Multi AZ

                               Snap incremental

 

                Redshift Spectrum = processing power

 

# Amazon Open Search Service

                Successor to Elastic Search

                Search any field, even partially matches

                Two modes: managed cluster or serveless cluster

                Ingestion from Kiness Data Firehouse, IoT, Cloud Watch Logs

                Security Cognito, IAM, KMS, TLS

                Comes with Dashboards*

 

# EMR  - Elastic MapReduce

                Hadoop clusters (big data) to analyze and process data

                AS and integrated with Spot instances

                Apache Spark, HBase, Presto, Flink

 

                Use cases: data processing, ML, web indexing, big data

 

                Nodes Types

                               Master Node: Manage the cluster, coordinate, manage health

                               Core node: Run task and store data – long running

                               Task node: Just to run task  - Use spot

 

                QuickSight

                               Serveless ML, BI service to create dashboard

                               Fast automatically scalable, embeddable

                               Integrate with RDS, Aurora, Athena, Redshift, S3

 

# Glue

                Manage extract, transform and load (ETL)

                Fully serveless

                Useful to prepare and transform data for analytics

 

                Glue Job Bookmarks: prevent re-processing data

                    “   Elastic View: Combine and replicate data across multiple data stores using SQL

                   “    DataBrew: clean and normalize data

                   “    Studio: Create new GUI

                  “    Streaming ETL: built on Apache Spark compatible with Kiness Data Streaming, Kafka, MSK (managed kafka)

 

# Lake Formation

                Data lake = Central place to have all data for analytics purposes

 

# Kiness data Analytics

                Real-time analytics on Kiness Data Streams & Firehouse

                Fully managed

 

                Output

                               Kiness Data Streams: create streams out of the real-time

                               “              “             Firehouse: send analytics quert results to destinations

 

                Use cases:

                               Time-series Analytics

                               Real-time dashboard

                               Real-time metrics